<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> 2) The penalty isn't just experience, it's con points too, which costs money.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Check my #2 again. I stated if you got a rez you would not be subjected to any greater death penalty than a few xp lost. You do NOT lose con if you get a rez. The death does count against you for the number of con you lose the next time you die without a rez, but you lose none if rezzed.<br>
