<br>
You will NOT lose the components you use to make an item if your tradeskill combine attempt fails.<br>
<br>
Which is not exactly true.  You don't lose components on all failures.  You don't even lose them on most.  BUT, you WILL lose components in trades from time to time.<br>
<br>
The other night I burned 5(!) oaken trident hafts and 2(!) steel trident heads, making one steel trident.  And those losses didnt' include the haft and head that ended up in the end item.  And for those keeping score...that was over 4.5g burned :)  Damn those high orange consignments.<br>
